<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Capulus camaranensis Sturany, 1903, Locality 43 (Kamaran Island, Yemen, Red Sea). A-E. Figured syntype, NHMW 37797: left side (A-B), protoconch (C), aperture (D), top (E). F. Post-metamorphic stage attached to Goniocidaris canaliculata (A. Agassiz, 1863). G. Original figure by Sturany (1903). H. Original label. Scale bars: A-B, D-F: 1 mm, C: 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118639" .

